caption.p: Analysis of common DEGs and metabolites among SASCs, EASCs, and PASCs. (A) Enriched GO terms of common DEGs among SASCs, EASCs, and PASCs. (B) Enriched KEGG pathways of common DEGs. (C) Analysis of metabolic pathways of common differential metabolites among SASCs, EASCs, and PASCs. (D) Top 25 enrichment of common differential metabolites.
